{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|茻|t1=grass|死|t2=dead person|ls=ic}} – bury the dead 死 in the grass 茻. Top is now grass radical ({{zh-l|艹|tr=-}}), while bottom is simplified to [[廾]], hence graphically {{Han compound|艸|死|廾|alt1=艹}}.

